{"type":"message","id":"e3ae0a9a","parentId":"93ea97bf","timestamp":"2026-03-08T23:06:26.480Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-03-09 07:06 GMT+8] please review and validate/update skills, /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/skills/context-anchor/SKILL.md and /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/skills/trustskill/SKILL.md , to adapt to your needs, then make sure it is recorded in your long term context memory."}],"timestamp":1773011186477}}
